Old old empire - Antailian Empire - monotheistic empire, last one before the socrerous revolution
Sorc. revolution resulted in people stopping god worship, gods left
City states ruled by powerful mages, eventually went to war with each other over philosophical differences
Many of their cities built in what was known as the Tropean Wastes
The big big war resulted in the world being rent - called the cataclysm
Massive collapse of society for the most part, Dawnridge was relatively protected
